# Worker Loop: graph-loop (P2)

Parent: `llm-wiki-mission-loop`

## Goal

Generate `.reasonix/graph.json` from catalog feature-lists; expose GET /api/graph; ship minimal Project Map UI.

## Read before touching code

1. `docs/p2-graph-artifact/14-implementation-plan.zh.md`
2. `docs/p2-graph-artifact/15-verification-plan.zh.md`
3. `state/phase.md`

## Iterate

1. State which P2 gate (G0–G3) this advances.
2. Smallest diff; one primary variable per PR.
3. Verify:

```bash
npm run typecheck
npm run catalog:gen && npm run graph:gen
npm test -- tests/graph-generate tests/routes-graph
npm test
npm run build:frontend   # Phase 3 only
```

## Stop signals

Use `done` when gate commands for the touched phase pass.
Use `blocked-needs-platform` if catalog feature-lists missing and cannot run catalog:gen.
